WEAPON SELECT SCREEN-
Weapon name (scroll -right- w/controller).
 Numbers represent WEIGHT and LENGTH of blade


KATANA - two handed, average attack speed, balanced attack power.
RAPIER - one handed, lightest weapon, ideal for thrust attacks, low defense.
NAGINATA - two handed, very slow attack speed, longest of all weapons, average attack power.
HAMMER - two handed, slow attack speed, VERY heavy. High attack power.
NODACHI - two handed, wider cutting surface, well balanced attack power, slower attack speed.
LONG SWORD - one handed weapon, faster attack speed, ideal for beginners.
SABER - shortest sword, one handed, fastest attack speed, low attack power.
BROAD SWORD - two handed, heavy sword, slow attack speed, good attack power because of double edged design.


